arraycomparison -> compare between different chips (just load data in and plot)
bapixelwise -> scatter plot dcr before and after (irradiation/annealing) 
beforeandaftermedian -> median plot of dcr before/after (irradiation/annealing)
cuml -> dcr cumulative for a chip
mediandcrbias -> classic median dcr vs bias (same as array comparison kinda but all loaded data from before irradiation)
